OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain clearing Caithness
OL,6,Fin the morning. This leaves a mostly
OL,7,Fcloudy day with scattered showers
OL,8,Fthroughout. Showers will be heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes. The best of any bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspells will be in the east, towards
OL,11,FMoray.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA largely cloudy evening with
OL,14,Fshowers, these heavy at first but
OL,15,Fgradually easing. Some clear spells
OL,16,Fovernight before cloud and patchy
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain spread northwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
