OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cloudy day with some
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning but
OL,7,Fmany parts staying dry. Outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain becoming more widespread in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with some heavy downpours
OL,10,Fpossible.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy Tuesday but with bright
OL,14,Fintervals and showers. Bright spells
OL,15,Fand showers at first Wednesday, heavy
OL,16,Frain later. Mostly cloudy with heavy
OL,17,Fshowers on Thursday. Breezy Wednesday
OL,18,Fand Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
